description:
This Fractals Skill will give you information about Guild Wars 2 Fractals.
You can get the Daily Fractals list, fractal name by level, or the recommended level for a given AR value.
You can also find out the materials to craft a specific Agony Infusion.

Ask things like
- Alexa, ask Fractals about today
- Alexa, ask Fractals about Level 40
- Alexa, ask Fractals about Agony 56
- Alexa, ask Fractals how do I make a +10 infusion?
name: Fractals Info
shortDescription: Which Fractal is Level 47?  This is a quick reference to Guild Wars 2 Fractals by level or  recommended agony resistance, and for Daily Fractals.
